{
  "stem": "2118.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And little by little, the ghetto got rid of all the troublemakers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like, people who got up and made speeches about this and about that, they were all sent out from the ghetto into labor camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the ghetto was, how would you say it, kept docile or made quiet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, there was no resistance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, the ghetto was ringed around with barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Being in the middle of the city and not having any big fields open, is what they put a wire on one side of the street.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then there was the street itself, and a wire, and the opposite sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was, like, a no man's land in between.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So if you-- to get out, in other words, you had to go through two fences.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in that middle, no man's land, around maybe every 100 yards, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] within seeing distance from each other, was a soldier with-- with a gun.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they put up those little houses, you know, like a soldier to be inside when it snows or rains-- like a watch house, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like a booth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like a booth, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were the soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the beginning, we walked along those sidewalks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then the Germans started shooting just for the fun of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people got shot just trying to walk on-- on the sidewalk which was right near the fence.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people didn't walk anymore those sidewalks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But from yards to yards were made holes in walls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it became like, if you wanted to go from one street to the other, you didn't even have to go to the street.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You went from this yard to this yard to this yard to this yard.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
